{"tid":299399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫收視全面插水","createTime":"2017-06-27T05:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T05:19:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35f4965d76f0914d2677120b111a985c92ed9b7c","tid":299399,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170627/20069595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170627%2F20069595&d=%2BU4DPnDw0U%2F5gYyF12vnWZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=7a620027\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170627%2F20069595&h=dcefc6ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170627/20069595</a><br />\n<br />\n無綫收視全面插水<br />\n<br />\n95,980<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n ■無綫的《六點半新聞報道》上周流失約21萬觀眾，慘不忍睹。電視圖片<br />\n■無綫的《六點半新聞報道》上周流失約21萬觀眾，慘不忍睹。電視圖片<br />\n無綫新聞經常被批評是是但但，令到觀眾離棄，早年開始周六與周日的《六點半新聞報道》，已經試過跌到單位數收視，想不到上周一至五的收視，亦跌至近年新低點單位數，平均收視只得9.7點，約63萬觀眾，比之前一周下跌3.2點，流失約21萬觀眾，認真慘不忍睹。<br />\n另外，無綫上周播映的內地劇《三生三世十里桃花》，同樣收視慘淡，平均收視12.7點，約82萬5千觀眾，比對上一周流失16萬9千觀眾。至於之後播出的《東張西望》、《愛．回家之開心速遞》及內地劇《射鵰英雄傳》同樣收視插水。<br />\n撰文：魯吉  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n古巨基密運婚紗娶助手　發哥發嫂趁拍戲空檔註冊<br />\n下一則<br />\n嚴選亞洲十大女神　冠軍唔係韓女星？"},{"pid":"b2dd5ca29a7b3a73f8a43f3f41b85d12b9e6d8c6","tid":299399,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170627/large/27ec2p60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F27ec2p60.jpg&h=a1210e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■無綫的《六點半新聞報道》上周流失約21萬觀眾，慘不忍睹。電視圖片"},{"pid":"f693a7c3fe009817e9d71637e2efaa0c4d5b695e","tid":299399,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:1